	18 May 2005 DK <dk@ossim.net> :
	* 0.9.8 released.

* OSSIM-0.9.8 (18 May 2005)

	05 May 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* Agent: restart plugins every X seconds, 
	  configurable via /etc/ossim/agent/config.xml plugin-restart.

    04 May 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* Close alarms at alarm console

	29 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
