	* Fixed some php notices on login startup

	25 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* www/host/newhost.php: inserting new host, update host info when host
	  exists in database.

	20 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* etc/logrotate.d/ossim-agent, etc/logrotate.d/ossim-framework:
	  Ossim framework and agent logrotate configuration files.
	* contrib/snort/snort_debian_config.patch, etc/agent/plugins/snort.xml:
	  Move /var/log/snort/fast.log references to /var/log/snort/alert.

	18 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* include/ossim_conf.inc: better use of trim reading config lines from
	  framework/ossim.conf.
	  (Thanks João)
	* contrib/patches/05_parser_ntsyslog_regexp_fix.patch
	  (Thanks Sébastien Contreras)
	* etc/logrotate.d/ossim-server: Ossim server logrotate configuration file

	14 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* agent/pyossim/ParserSnareWindows.py: snare for windows support improved.
	* www/netscan/index.php: fixed error with javascript and IExplorer.
	* www/editor/rule.php: fixed error in snort rule viewer with 
	  snort_rules_dir without trailing slash.
	* www/vulnmeter/index.php: removed ugly warnings in Vulnmeter.
	* contrib/patches/05_restart_parserSnort_to_avoid_logrotate_fd_changes.patch

	13 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
