	  rrdtool outputs. This solves strange erros with some rrds.
	* contrib/patches/05_average_service_level_day.patch

	11 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* Merge etc/ and debian/ config files
	* contrib directory cleanup
	* contrib/patches/05_more_net_perms_by_user.patch

	07 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* Acid Cache: there was a problem fetching acid pages with GET attributes.
	  Replace & with %26 html entity solved the problem.

	06 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* include/classes/Session.inc: rename getValue() method to allowedNets() 
	  (why did we called getValue?).
	* contrib/acid|base/*.patch: use new allowedNets() method.
	* www/*: use new allowedNets() method.

	05 Apr 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* contrib/snort/snort_debian_config.patch: automatic debian configuration
	  for snort packages

	30 Mar 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* debian/INSTALL.html: Debian install guide rewritten in html+css

	28 Mar 2005 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
	* Base (Acid replacement) integration:
	  Be careful with the following framework options:
	   - alert_viewer (NEW)
	   - acid_link
	   - acid_path
	* agent/pyossim/ParserArpwatch:
	  Arpwatch fixes (thanks to ossim-help forum folks).
	* frameworkd/ossimframework/ControlPanel.py:
	  Clean up rrd directory deleting unused rrd files. This will minimize the
	  execution time of frameworkd iterations.

